name: THE TICKLE - Issue #32 Kazuhiro Aihara Special Edition
description:
Special 1/1 edition of Issue #32. Art zine focused on Hic et Nunc artists and writers.

Issue #32 features artists Hexeosis (@hexeosis), Lucia Delfino (@muyseniora) & Kazuhiro Aihara (@kazuhiroaihara), with poetry by Katerina Watson (@katerina_writes).

Created by artist Wily Guys (@guyswily) with help from Theo Horsmeier (@THorsmeier) and Joanne Rush (@JonicolaRush).
